  "note": "Madhhab-level rule module (pure data). The Shafi'is (with the Malikis) hold that profit in a capital partnership must track the capital ratio — hence this module REQUIRES `profit_tracks_capital`, diverging from the Hanafi/Hanbali modules. Citations from al-Shafi'i (al-Umm) and al-Nawawi (al-Majmu'); flagged [scholar-verify].",
